{"tid":666803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主席馬時亨:加價是公開、客觀具透明度, 不反映事實的報道會令同事難過 強調無錢點維修?","createTime":"2018-05-16T07:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T09:51:17.000Z","uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf5e0ba07f8fff8e7826b362f442263b62d21ca","tid":666803,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:44:41.000Z","msg":"港鐵主席馬時亨於股東周年大會致辭時表示，明白有市民對港鐵票價有爭論，希望愈平愈好，但票價調整機制是公開、客觀與具透明度，港鐵要有穩定收入才能繼續投放資源在更新、維修鐵路資產。 他又說，自兩鐵合併後香港平均通3.2%，同期香港薪金指數平均每年上升4.4%，兩者都高於港鐵同期票價平均增幅2.5%，港鐵每年用七至八成經常性利潤以股息回饋股東，政府亦收到可觀股息。 馬時亨又說，團隊積極為市民服務，機器總有壞的時候，同事每次都竭盡所能，會接受善意批評，加以改善。但不公平、不反映事實的報道會令同事難過，影響團隊士氣，他亦對苛刻的指責感到難過。"},{"pid":"6e20d1fdf932985bfc36c0c03874b5db3dfacd33","tid":666803,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21c0ffad206e83f7d5f2e64f98e302af9c04c25","tid":666803,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">團隊積極為市民服務，機器總有壞的時候，同事每次都竭盡所能，會接受善意批評</span>"},{"pid":"f1b52e2fb870faf213d73ad256ba6c39fa90ed22","tid":666803,"uid":38376,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"其實最應該凍薪<br />\n<br />\n一班人維修港鐵維修到成日壞<br />\n<br />\nd司機開車睇書睇電話剪腳甲，連關門都懶得睇，一個星期最少一次有人被夾而司機等過世咁唔開門，都唔知等乜7，唔係打機冇睇住真係搵鬼信<br />\n<br />\n然後到d高層，一日到黑諗d鋪位點增加，廁所又冇，育嬰室冇，d新站連客務中心都cut埋。反而書店衫店便利店麵包店連賣電器都全齊<br />\n<br />\n我覺得全體職員減薪差唔多"},{"pid":"2fae7dad6bec4f4fcb42a9440408325da608e2c9","tid":666803,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"一年賺百幾億都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe91bbb9caf7eb8f82c1f671b05b790b5cc09fe","tid":666803,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a21c0ffad206e83f7d5f2e64f98e302af9c04c25","tid":666803,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:47:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">團隊積極為市民服務，機器總有壞的時候，同事每次都竭盡所能，會接受善意批評</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:04:04.000Z","msg":"''會接受善意批評''<br />\n睇到火都黎<br />\n即係想同你講<br />\n你今次係有唔啱<br />\n做好啲乖喇喎<br />\n下次唔好<br />\n香港攪撚成咁"},{"pid":"15d930e3b5f362826c3a98000d57336810715f2f","tid":666803,"uid":48964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:06:26.000Z","msg":"He's given a second life after cancer.. and still lives as a douchebag <br />\n<br />\nKarma will come"},{"pid":"93616a78de8cb4e448a0050712bdd20f3df98a74","tid":666803,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fae7dad6bec4f4fcb42a9440408325da608e2c9","tid":666803,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"一年賺百幾億都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:20:43.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母, 一年百幾億都冇錢維修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  用太空船載客呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b65547220632caa75de3d3259e85fccbb852b35","tid":666803,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"講到唔加價就冇收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死肥佬真係癌上腦 夾硬混淆收入同盈利<br />\n而家地鐵係扣除晒所有成本都賺緊億億聲<br />\n起親新線都有政府批地 冇地就政府科水(e.g.沙中線)<br />\n投資地產仲多過鐵路產業R&amp;D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7006cf5d87d4012c9574ae96995b93bd3f7417c","tid":666803,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"EBITDA:<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/images/investor/finhighlight_optprofit_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://